in%20the%20makeup%20world%20in%20the%20weeks%20before%20his%20death.%20On%20July%201%2C%20the%20UK-based%20makeup%20brand%20Jolie%20Beauty%20announced%20it%20was%20partnering%20with%20the%20rock%20legend%20and%20launching%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjoliebeauty.co.uk%2Fcollections%2Fozzy-osbourne%3Fsrsltid%3DAfmBOoo5WAo6XPvzhmdN_AlKmS5lT2TK6Yl9TeInorOQS0q2H5Iq6SfW%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimited-edition%20collection%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECustomers%20could%20preorder%20the%20entire%20collection%2C%20which%20included%20brushes%2C%20lipsticks%2C%20and%20a%20makeup%20bag%20emblazoned%20with%20an%20Osbourne-esque%20skull%2C%20for%20%24553.%20The%20CEO%20of%20the%20Birmingham-based%20company%20said%20in%20a%20video%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Freel%2F1284518679691378%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFacebook%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20opportunity%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Babsolute%20honor%2C%26quot%3B%20noting%20that%20Osbourne%20himself%20was%20from%20Birmingham%2C%20England.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Liquid%20Death%20and%20Jolie%20Beauty%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20Osbourne%20starred%20in%20the%20MTV%20reality%20show%20%26quot%3BThe%20Osbournes%26quot%3B%20alongside%20his%20wife%20and%20kids.%20His%20somewhat%20unconventional%20business%20partnerships%20weren't%20entirely%20new%2C%20either%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0in%202003%2C%20Chipotle%20created%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-chipotle-celebrity-card-how-do-you-get-one-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChipotle%20Celebrity%20Card%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20him%2C%20which%20grants%20unlimited%20Chipotle%20for%20one%20year.%20As%20of%202022%2C%20he%20was%20the%20only%20lifelong%20cardholder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOsbourne%20struggled%20with%20Parkinson's%20disease%20in%20the%20final%20years%20of%20his%20