t%20took%20me%20nearly%20an%20hour%20to%20find%20the%20tour%20group's%20small%20black%20flag%20beside%20the%20Arch%20of%20Constantine%20outside%20the%20Colosseum's%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Viator%20representative%20apologized%20for%20the%20confusion%2C%20telling%20BI%20that%20the%20issue%20stems%20from%20tourist%20hot%20spots%20becoming%20increasingly%20congested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELuckily%2C%20I%20found%20the%20small%20black%20flag%20just%20in%20time%20for%20my%20scheduled%20entry%20time%2C%20but%20not%20without%20a%20bit%20of%20stress%20first.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20the%20tour%20meet-up%20spot%20and%20the%20author's%20ticket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fbab885e81483682e7252%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20finds%20her%20tour%20group%20and%20retrieves%20her%20ticket.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20finally%20found%20my%20tour%20guide%2C%20she%20handed%20me%20my%20ticket%20for%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20my%20ticket%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20skip%20the%20general%20admission%20line%2C%20but%20I%20still%20had%20to%20wait%20in%20a%20relatively%20short%20line%20to%20be%20admitted%20and%20go%20through%20a%20security%20checkpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20inside%2C%20I%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20where%20I%20found%20people%20shoving%20and%20cutting%20each%20other%20in%20line.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20bathroom%20line%20and%20crowds%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fbaf385e81483682e725f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom%20line%20and%20a%20crowded%20space%20inside%20the%20Colosseum.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20encountered%20people%20pushing%20each%20other%20forward%20and%20arguing%20about%20who%20was%20in%20line%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20woman%20took%20her%20whole%20tour%20group%20and%20pushed%20to%20the%20front%20of%20the%20line%2C%20cutting%20several%20people%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20my%20turn%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%2C%20another%20woman%20shoved%20me%20forward%20as%20soon%20as%20a%20stall%20opened%20up%20before%20I%20even%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20truly%20shocked%20at%20how%20people%20behaved%20in%20this%20situation%2C%20and%20it%20soured%20my%20experience%20at%20the%20historical%20landmark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAfter%20my%20half-hour%20ordeal%20of%20waiting%20to%20use%20the%20bathroom%2C%20I%20finally%20got%20to%20see%20the%20epic%20view%20of%20the%20arena%20inside%20the%20Colosseum's%20walls%20...%20sort%20of.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowds%20of%20people%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20arena%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fbb4e3d5881a51c1dc440%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20wait%20to%20take%20pictures%20in%20front%20of%20the%20arena%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20too%20many%20people%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20to%20walk%20up%20to%20the%20edge%20of%20the%20stands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20people%20formed%20lines%20in%20front%20of%20each%20viewpoint%20to%20get%20a%20glance%20at%20the%20arena%20below%20and%20take%20a%20picture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20waiting%20for%20my%20turn%2C%20I%20stood%20on%20my%20tippy%20toes%20to%20see%20the%20Colosseum%20above%20rows%20of%20heads%20that%20obscured%20my%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20each%20viewpoint%2C%20I%20waited%20in%20line%20for%20five%20to%2010%20minutes%20to%20see%20the%20arena%20for%20what%20felt%20like%2015%20seconds%20before%20people%20rushed%20up%20to%20take%20my%20place.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Groups%20of%20travelers%20pose%20for%20pictures%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fbb933d5881a51c1dc44d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETourists%20take%20photos%20at%20the%20Colosseum.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20I%20wanted%20a%20few%20moments%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20to%20tap%20into%20my%20creativity%20and%20visualize%20the%20fights%20that%20happened%20in%20Ancient%20Rome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20were%20too%20many%20people%20trying%20to%20take%20my%20place%20for%20me%20to%20have%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20I%20had%20my%20turn%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20edge%20overlooking%20the%20arena%2C%20I%20noticed%20the%20Colosseum%20was%20under%20restoration%2C%20which%20wasn't%20the%20most%20stunning%20view.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20a%20ladder%20and%20scaffolding%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fb0e8f748d8c055f60aa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERestoration%20at%20the%20Colosseum.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20restoration%20I%20saw%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20made%20it%20feel%20like%20one%20big%20construction%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20understand%20that%20old%20buildings%20often%20need%20to%20be%20restored%20to%20last%20hundreds%20of%20years%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20current%20work%20on%20the%20Colosseum%20will%20improve%20the%20visitor%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202021%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2021%2F05%2F03%2F993184621%2Froman-colosseums-new-floor-will-give-visitors-a-gladiators-point-of-view%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENPR%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Colosseum%20planned%20to%20open%20a%20floor-level%20attraction%20by%202023.%20The%20attraction%20would%20allow%20visitors%20to%20enter%20the%20arena%20on%20a%20retractable%20floor%20and%20get%20a%20gladiator's%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20haven't%20seen%20reports%20on%20the%20site's%20opening%20to%20the%20general%20public.%20Still%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarpediemtours.com%2Frome%2Fcolosseum-tour-with-underground-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECarpe%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcarpediemtours.com%2Frome%2Fcolosseum-tour-with-underground-access%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDiem%20Tours%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20VIP%20Colosseum%20excursion%20with%20access%20to%20select%20spaces%2C%20including%20the%20arena%20floor%20and%20underground%20tunnels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EExhibits%20about%20the%20structure's%20history%20were%20just%20as%20packed%20as%20the%20viewpoints%2C%20and%20I%20quickly%20gave%20up%20trying%20to%20view%20them.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowds%20of%20people%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20exhibits%20at%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fbbc485e81483682e7290%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222880%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrowds%20around%20the%20Colosseum's%20exhibits.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20view%20the%20Colosseum's%20exhibits%2C%20I%20shuffled%20along%20slowly%20with%20a%20crowd%2C%20simultaneously%20taking%20in%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%20before%20people%20began%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20exhibits%20were%20more%20packed%20than%20almost%20any%20museum%20I've%20been%20to%2C%20and%20I%20only%20viewed%20them%20for%20about%2015%20minutes%20before%20I%20became%20frustrated%20and%20gave%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20four-story%20structure%20also%20offered%20views%20of%20surrounding%20sites%2C%20but%20those%20areas%20were%20just%20as%20crowded.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Crowds%20inside%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%20in%20October%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fac2f3d5881a51c1dc1e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECrowds%20inside%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%20in%20October%202022.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20time%20to%20visit%20the%20nearby%20attractions.%20So%20I%20was%20excited%20that%20the%20Colosseum's%20interior%20also%20has%20views%20of%20surrounding%20Ancient%20Roman%20sites%2C%20like%20the%20Roman%20Forum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20found%20that%20these%20areas%20were%20just%20as%20crowded%20as%20the%20arena%20viewpoints%2C%20and%20since%20I'm%205'3%26quot%3B%2C%20I%20couldn't%20see%20past%20other%20tourists%20and%20their%20outstretched%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EI%20still%20want%20my%20quiet%20moment%20to%20walk%20the%20Colosseum%20floor%20and%20feel%20like%20a%20gladiator.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225022%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20visits%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20October%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63d7f33bfc184700195550dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223766%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20reporter%20visits%20the%20Colosseum%20in%20Rome%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20October%202022.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20