3A%2F%2Fwww.af.mil%2FNews%2FArticle-Display%2FArticle%2F4241485%2Fair-force-battle-lab-advances-the-kill-chain-with-ai-c2-innovation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20order%20to%20have%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-allies-ai-target-enemies-like-would-war-first-time-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emore%20automated%20kill%20chain%20in%20a%20potential%20future%20fight%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20four-day%20Experiment%203%20exercise%2C%20held%20last%20month%2C%20was%20a%20stress%20test%20of%20future%20warfare%20technologies%20and%20tactics%20in%20a%20realistic%20combat%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20replicating%20this%20novel%20methodology%2C%20we%20allowed%20tactical-level%20participants%20to%20explore%20how%20tools%20and%20workflows%20could%20shape%20kill%20chain%20execution%20for%20the%20future%20of%20warfighting%2C%26quot%3B%20Lt.%20Col.%20Wesley%20Schultz%2C%20the%20director%20of%20operations%20for%20the%20805th%20Combat%20Training%20Squadron%2FShadow%20Operations%20Center-Nellis%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20kill%20chain%20is%20a%20military%20decision%20process%20that%20guides%20how%20forces%20detect%20a%20threat%2C%20zero%20in%20on%20it%2C%20act%2C%20and%20evaluate%20the%20outcome.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20US%20military%20is%20actively%20looking%20to%20evolve%20its%20kill%20chain%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-agents-coming-military-new-scaleai-contract-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eautomation%2C%20AI%2C%20data-driven%3C%2Fa%3E%20command%20and%20control%20decisions%2C%20and%20interconnected%C2%A0sensors%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20training%2C%20operators%20used%20AI%20software%20to%20accelerate%20decision-making%20and%20targeting%20processes.%20It%20was%20designed%20to%20speed%20up%20those%20processes%20and%20%26quot%3Breduce%20the%20cognitive%20load%26quot%3B%20on%20human%20operators%2C%20the%20service%20said%20in%20a%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Secretary%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%20Frank%20Kendall%20flies%20in%20an%20X-62A%20VISTA%20in%20the%20skies%20above%20Edwards%20Air%20Force%20Base%2C%20Calif.%2C%20May%202%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6674323da76074d191cd56a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20and%20other%20military%20programs%20have%20been%20working%20on%20unmanned%20aircraft%20than%20can%20fly%20alongside%20piloted%20aircraft%20or%20on%20their%20own.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Richard%20Gonzales%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EReducing%20the%20cognitive%20load%2C%20or%20mental%20effort%2C%20of%20warfighting%20personnel%20has%20become%20a%20priority%2C%20especially%20in%20recent%20years%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20AI.%20US%20military%20leaders%20and%20officials%20believe%20that%20AI%20can%20assist%20humans%20in%20assessing%20massive%20amounts%20of%20battlefield%20data%20to%20help%20make%20clearer%20decisions%20more%20quickly.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20used%20was%20developed%20under%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-executive-compared-project-maven-to-manhattan-project-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMaven%20Smart%20System%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20larger%20US%20military%20AI%20initiative.%20During%20testing%2C%20the%20assessments%20made%20only%20by%20operators%20were%20compared%20to%20those%20made%20with%20AI%20recommendations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testing%20was%20intended%20to%20explore%20the%20value%20of%20human-machine%20teaming.%20%26quot%3BDifferences%20between%20machine-generated%20recommendations%20and%20operator%20decisions%20highlighted%20the%20complementary%20strengths%20of%20human%20judgment%2C%20such%20as%20intuition%2C%20experience%20and%20situational%20awareness%2C%20in%20time-sensitive%20targeting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20service%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeedback%20from%20the%20exercise%2C%20as%20well%20as%20observations%20of%20how%20the%20AI%20operated%2C%20was%20then%20used%20to%20refine%20systems%20and%20processes.%C2%A0Former%20Secretary%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%20Frank%20Kendall%20said%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20future%20warfare%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20automated%2C%20highly%20autonomous%2C%20action%20at%20long%20range%2C%20precision%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20space%20will%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bdecisive%20theater%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bresponse%20times%20to%20bring%20effects%20to%20bear%20are%20very%20short%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20in%20a%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffuture-warfighting-decisions-inhuman-speeds-air-force-secretary-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edecisions%20will%20not%20be%20made%20at%20human%20speed%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20they're%20going%20to%20be%20made%20at%20machine%20speed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20year%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-china-new-technology-race-air-force-secretary-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emastery%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E%20solutions%20could%20be%20key%20to%20winning%20the%20next%20major%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225634%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20wearing%20an%20Army%20camouflage%20uniform%20kneels%20on%20one%20knee%20holding%20a%20drone%20controller%20in%20his%20hands.%20A%20quadcopter%20drone%20is%20on%20the%20ground%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20Behind%20the%20man%20is%20a%20line%20of%20green%20trees.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F683dc310c6ad288d14824f9d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224507%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAI%20is%20being%20implemented%20acro