0tight-grip%20lifts%20like%20deadlifts%2C%20where%20it%20can%20chafe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220158cc3c-ad42-44d7-8f1a-6c40182e6841%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Oura%20Ring%203%20vs.%20Oura%20Ring%204%5C%22%3EOura%20Ring%203%20vs.%20Oura%20Ring%204%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20thinking%20of%20saving%20a%20few%20bucks%20and%20just%20getting%20a%20previous%20generation%20of%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20%E2%80%94%20don't.%20The%20Oura%20Ring%204%20is%20a%20significant%20improvement%20over%20the%20Oura%20Ring%203%2C%20and%20each%20upgrade%20is%20worth%20every%20penny.%20Compared%20to%20the%20Oura%20Ring%203%2C%20the%20Oura%20Ring%204%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHas%20a%20sleeker%20design%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIs%20more%20comfortable%20to%20wear%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIs%20now%20made%20entirely%20out%20of%20titanium%20on%20both%20the%20interior%20and%20exterior%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHas%20a%20new%20dynamic%20%26quot%3Bsmart%20sensing%26quot%3B%20technology%20that%20uses%20more%20sensors%20and%20pathways%20(18%20vs.%20the%20previous%208)%20to%20drop%20the%20signal%20less%2C%20giving%20you%20more%20continuous%20tracking%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHas%20longer%20battery%20life%20at%20eight%20days%20vs.%20seven%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20features%20make%20Oura%20Ring%204%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20best%20smart%20ring%2C%20and%20they're%20well%20worth%20the%20%2450%20price%20difference%20between%20a%20Gen%203%20ring%20and%20a%20Gen%204%20ring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22504eb4da-d09e-47b8-81c6-f1a3a11170db%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Key%20features%5C%22%3EThe%20health%20metrics%20that%20matter%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20screenshots%20from%20the%20oura%20app.%20the%20first%20panel%20shows%20the%20main%20stats%20screen%20with%20activity%20goal%20progress%20and%20the%20second%20panel%20shows%20a%20close%20up%20of%20the%20movement%20screen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fd402f748d8c055f6101a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOura's%20app%20is%20sleek%20and%20well-designed%2C%20with%20clear%20metrics%20at%20a%20glance%20that%20you%20can%20tap%20into%20to%20get%20more%20data.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20smart%20ring%20category%2C%20each%20brand%20offers%20different%20data%20and%20insights.%20I%20tested%20smart%20rings%20alongside%20some%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-fitness-tracker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20fitness%20trackers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20impressed%20to%20find%20the%20sleep%20quality%2C%20step%20count%2C%20and%20readiness%20insights%20to%20be%20highly%20accurate%20on%20the%20Oura%204.%20What's%20more%2C%20I%20found%20that%20Oura's%20app%20kept%20the%20metrics%20streamlined%20to%20the%20info%20I%20wanted%20most%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%2C%20most%20notably%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleep%20accuracy%20and%20insights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Oura%20gives%20you%20an%20at-a-glance%20sleep%20score%2C%20with%20your%20total%20sleep%20time%20front%20and%20center.%20Click%20in%20and%20it%20offers%20more%20detailed%20insights%2C%20like%20sleep%20efficiency%2C%20total%20restfulness%2C%20and%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20fall%20asleep.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESleeping%20heart%20rate%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20ring%20measures%20when%20your%20heart%20rate%20hits%20its%20lowest%20during%20the%20night%2C%20which%20can%20give%20insight%20into%20how%20recovered%20(or%20not)%20your%20body%20is.%20I%20found%20it%20very%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20alcohol%20and%20staying%20up%20unusually%20late%20affected%20this.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ESkin%20temperature%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Pretty%20standard%20on%20wearables%20these%20days.%20Changes%20in%20your%20skin%20temperature%20can%20signal%20you're%20about%20to%20get%20sick.%20There%20were%20a%20handful%20of%20days%20I%20woke%20up%20with%20an%20alert%20in%20elevated%20skin%20temperature%2C%20heeded%20the%20Oura%20advisor's%20advice%20to%20rest%20rather%20than%20push%2C%20and%20potentially%20avoided%20getting%20more%20sick%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EReadiness%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Arguably%20the%20most%20helpful%20metric%20for%20active%20people%2C%20this%20recovery%20score%20pulls%20from%2020%2B%20signals%20%E2%80%94%20skin%20temp%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20more%20%E2%80%94%20to%20tell%20you%20whether%20to%20push%20or%20rest.%20Sure%2C%20you%20%3Cem%3Ecould%3C%2Fem%3E%20just%20listen%20to%20your%20body%2C%20but%20I%20found%20it%20genuinely%20helpful%20to%20get%20a%20concrete%20reflection%20that%20rest%20was%20smarter.%20More%20than%20once%2C%20I%20woke%20at%206%3A30%20a.m.%20for%20my%20morning%20workout%2C%20only%20to%20see%20my%20skin%20temp%20was%20up%20or%20sleep%20was%20off%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Oura%20told%20me%20to%20take%20it%20easy%20instead.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EWomen's%20health%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOne%20of%20Oura's%20standout%20features%20for%20women%20is%20how%20it%20combines%20its%20advanced%20skin%20temperature%20tracking%20with%20its%20AI%20module%20to%20learn%20your%20menstrual%20cycle%20and%20offer%20detailed%20insights%20into%20your%20phases%2C%20variability%2C%20and%20when%20to%20expect%20your%20period.%20It%20functions%20pretty%20much%20like%20a%20basal%20body%20temp%20tracker%20(though%20not%20%26quot%3Bofficially%26quot%3B)%20and%20can%20even%20pinpoint%20your%20ovulation%20period%20and%20fertile%20window.%20If%20you're%20pregnant%2C%20it%20tracks%20your%20progress%2C%20highlights%20key%20physiological%20changes%2C%20and%20shares%20helpful%20educational%20content%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBiohacking%20insights%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20More%20recently%2C%20Oura%20has%20started%20tracking%20longer-term%20measurements%20to%20predict%20things%20like%20your%20cardiovascular%20age%20and%20your%20cardio%20capacity%20(VO2%20max).%20This%20is%20meant%20to%20give%20you%20insight%20into%20longevity%2C%20as%20well%20as%20your%20overall%20%26quot%3Bresilience%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20essentially%20how%20efficiently%20your%20body%20is%20bouncing%20back%20from%20stress%20time%20and%20time%20again.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto%20activity%20detection%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Oura%20Ring%20is%20very%20good%20at%20detecting%20activity%20and%20movement.%20What's%20more%2C%20it%20has%20you%20verify%20what%20that%20mild%20spike%20in%20heart%20rate%20was%20at%2011%20a.m.%20(housework%3F%20walking%3F)%2C%20and%20then%20learns%20from%20this%20to%20better%20identify%20your%20activities%20over%20time.%20This%20may%20sound%20basic%2C%20but%20other%20smart%20rings%20I've%20tested%20do%20not%20pick%20up%20on%20Zone%202%20walks%20(I'd%20have%20to%20remember%20my%20start%20and%20finish%20time%20and%20then%20manually%20enter%20it)%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20small%20calorie%20burners%20that%20count%20toward%20daily%20movement%20like%20housework.%20That%20said%2C%20if%20you%20live%20at%20altitude%20like%20I%20do%2C%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20does%20think%20every%20activity%20is%20skiing%20until%20you%20train%20it%20otherwise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c0968005-509b-49b5-8609-8aac305468e4%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Other%20features%20I%20love%5C%22%3EOther%20features%20I%20love%20in%20the%20Oura%20Ring%204%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20two%20screenshots%20from%20the%20oura%20app.%20the%20first%20panel%20shows%20an%20alert%20telling%20the%20user%20to%20take%20it%20easy%20due%20to%20their%20readiness%20score%20and%20the%20second%20panel%20shows%20their%20sleep%20metrics%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fd4dd3d5881a51c1dc826%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere's%20a%20big%20focus%20on%20rest%20and%20readiness%20in%20the%20app.%20I%20appreciate%20that%20it%20alerts%20me%20when%20my%20biometrics%20show%20I%20should%20take%20it%20easy%20(left)%20and%20its%20sleep%20tracking%20is%20robust%20and%20helpful%20(right).%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%204%20has%20a%20few%20other%20features%20that%20make%20it%20a%20very%20worthy%20investment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20app%20interface%20is%20super%20streamlined.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENew%20in%202025%2C%20Oura%20revamped%20its%20app%20so%20it%20only%20has%20three%20tabs%3A%20Today%2C%20Vitals%2C%20and%20My%20Health.%20The%20data%20is%20well-organized%20and%20presented%20in%20a%20very%20clear%20and%20visually%20distinct%20format%20that%20I%20found%20to%20be%20easy%20to%20interpret%20at%20a%20glance.%20It%20was%20by%20far%20the%20most%20streamlined%20and%20intuitive%20app%20to%20read%20my%20health%20data%20among%20the%20four%20smart%20rings%20I%20tested.%20And%20considering%20this%20is%20a%20device%20that%20has%20no%20display%20itself%2C%20the%20app%20is%20half%20the%20product%20you're%20buying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20only%20have%20to%20charge%20it%20once%20a%20week.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20advantages%20of%20Oura%20over%20its%20competitors%20is%20the%20ring's%20eight-day%20battery%20life.%20I%20felt%20like%20every%20other%20model%20I%20tested%20needed%20to%20be%20charged%20every%20few%20days%2C%20but%20eight%20days%20of%20power%20really%20does%20feel%20like%20less%20of%20an%20inconvenience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20automatically%20adapts%20my%20goals%20when%20my%20biometrics%20indicate%20I%20need%20more%20rest%20and%20recovery.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20my%20readiness%20score%20is%2044%2F100%2C%20it%20adjusts%20my%20daily%20movement%20goal%20to%20be%204%2C500%20steps%20instead%20of%2012%2C000.%20And%20you%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20put%20the%20Oura%20app%20into%20%26quot%3Brest%20mode%26quot%3B%20if%20you're%20sick%2C%20wherein%20it%20turns%20off%20all%20targets%20and%20goals%20and%20just%20tracks%20your%20biometrics.%20I%20found%20these%20adjustments%20went%20a%20long%20way%20in%20helping%20me%20feel%20like%20I'm%20taking%20care%20of%20myself%20in%20a%20holistic%20way%2C%20resting%20when%20needed%2C%20rather%20than%20prompting%20me%20to%20get%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20when%20I%20was%20sick%20in%20bed%20with%20COVID%20like%20other%20smart%20rings%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIts%20AI%20insights%20are%20actually%20helpful.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Oura%20leans%20heavily%20on%20predictive%20technology%20to%20give%20you%20insight%20on%20when%20your%20biomarkers%20are%20indicating%20that%20you%20might%20get%20sick%20or%20your%20fertility%20window.%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20the%20brand%20also%20launched%20Oura%20Advisor%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20guidance%20tool%20where%20you%20can%20ask%20it%20questions%20on%20your%20menstrual%20cycle%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20and%20other%20personalized%20data%20results%20(e.g.%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20traveling%20for%20work%20and%20noticed%20my%20readiness%20score%20has%20gone%20down%20a%20lot.%20What%20can%20I%20do%20to%20get%20it%20back%20up%3F%26quot%3B).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eefd60d6-f53f-432b-aae5-a64928c9375c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Where%20it%20falls%20short%5C%22%3EWhere%20it%20falls%20short%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsights%20could%20be%20more%20actionable.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20does%20a%20great%20job%20at%20tracking%20your%20data%2C%20it%20doesn't%20provide%20a%20ton%20of%20actionable%20fixes%20behind%20it.%20Days%20where%20my%20readiness%20was%20low%2C%20it%20would%20tell%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20help%20recharge%20your%20energy%20levels%2C%20take%20it%20easy%20today!%26quot%3B%20without%20much%20specificity%20on%20what%20I%20could%20do%20to%20bring%20my%20numbers%20back%20up.%20Of%20course%2C%20I%20could%20then%20take%20another%20step%20and%20ask%20the%20Oura%20AI%20Advisor%20this%20question%2C%20but%20it'd%20be%20nice%20to%20have%20this%20already%20integrated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20requires%20a%20monthly%20subscription.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20addition%20to%20the%20%24350%20to%20%24500%20ring%20itself%20(the%20price%20depends%20on%20which%20finish%20you%20choose)%2C%20you%20do%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20%246%20per%20month%20subscription%20fee%20to%20use%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20features%20of%20your%20Oura%20Ring.%20(Technically%2C%20you%20can%20use%20the%20app%20for%20free%20and%20get%20readings%20on%20basic%20metrics%20%E2%80%94%20readiness%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20activity%20%E2%80%94%20but%20most%20people%20will%20want%20the%20upgrade.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20may%20not%20offer%20enough%20information%20for%20athletes.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20does%20cover%20most%20insights%20that%20a%20health%20and%20basic%20fitness%20tracker%20will%20give%20you%20%E2%80%94%20resting%20heart%20rate%2C%20daily%20calorie%20burn%2C%20sleep%20quality%2C%20recovery%20%E2%80%94%20it%20won't%20track%20your%20running%20mileage%20or%20pace%2C%20overall%20exertion%20during%20a%20strength%20session%2C%20or%20other%2C%20deeper%20training%20insights.%20Serious%20runners%20or%20athletes%20will%20still%20want%20a%20more%20robust%20fitness%20tracker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f20c58e8-da9a-489b-a5fb-6d32e7185402%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Who%20should%20buy%20it%5C%22%3EFinal%20call%3A%20Who%20this%20ring%20is%20(and%20isn't)%20for%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20hand%20wearing%20multiple%20rings%2C%20including%20the%20oura%204%2C%20resting%20on%20the%20wearer's%20leg%2C%20which%20is%20covered%20in%20a%20pinstripe%20pant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F687fd2f2f748d8c055f60ff4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Oura%20Ring%204%20is%20a%20great%20option%20for%20those%20who%20want%20a%20discreet%20fitness%20tracker.%3Cp%3ERachael%20Shultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20opinion%2C%20the%20Oura%20Ring%20is%20the%20best%20smart%20ring%20for%20most%20people%2C%20whether%20you're%20looking%20to%20improve%20your%20basic%20health%2C%20stay%20more%20active%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%20or%20have%20one%20device%20that%20gives%20you%20insight%20into%20every%20aspect%20of%20your%20health%2C%20from%20heart%20to%20menstrual.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20highly%20accurate%20at%20tracking%20steps%2C%20activity%2C%20sleep%20quality%2C%20and%20overall%20physiological%20rest%20and%20recovery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20considering%20smart%20rings%20vs.%20a%20health%20or%20fitness%20watch%2C%20the%20advantage%20of%20a%20smart%20ring%20is%20that%20it%20offers%20deeper%20health%20insights%20in%20a%20much%20more%20discreet%20design%2C%20with%20no%20sounds%20or%20vibration%20notification%20prompts%20on%20your%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20more%20of%20a%20biohacker%20health%20type%2C%20you'll%20probably%20prefer%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110068648aa-20%26h%3Dccb77b6f674524d21760b10704bf9cffe3754c4315854575f334889246429d4c%26postID%3D687e7deaf1b38408f3a949cc%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Foura-ring-4-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FULTRAHUMAN-Ring-AIR-FSA-Approved-Wearable%252Fdp%252FB0D983R3N3%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUltrahuman%20Ring%20AIR%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20if%20you%20want%20one%20wearable%20that%20offers%20more%20comprehensive%20fitness%20tracking%2C%20you'll%20be%20happier%20with%20a%20fitness%20watch%20like%20one%20of%20our%20picks%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-garmin-watch%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%2