e%20to%20national%20attention%20when%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20his%20programme%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMann%20Ki%20Baat%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20praised%20Jagdish%E2%80%99s%20efforts%2C%20a%20recognition%20that%20brought%20both%20joy%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20fulfilment%20to%20the%20humble%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagdish%E2%80%99s%20journey%20began%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20personal%20loss.%20He%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%2018%2C%20a%20pivotal%20moment%20in%20his%20life%20that%20left%20a%20deep%20impact.%20The%20tragedy%20could%20have%20crushed%20him%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20it%20became%20the%20catalyst%20for%20a%20life%20built%20around%20resilience%20and%20a%20deep%20connection%20to%20the%20earth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20age%20of%2020%2C%20I%20made%20a%20firm%20decision%20to%20honour%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20by%20doing%20something%20meaningful%20with%20the%20land%20he%20had%20left%20behind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20In%20addition%20to%20managing%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20farm%2C%20Jagdish%20also%20runs%20a%20small%20ration%20shop%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20another%20way%20he%20contributes%20to%20his%20village%E2%80%99s%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20disappointment%20to%20triumph%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201990%2C%20with%20no%20formal%20training%20but%20an%20unshakeable%20desire%20to%20improve%20his%20circumstances%2C%20Jagdish%20set%20out%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20plant%20fruit%20trees%20on%20his%20land.%20He%20began%20by%20planting%20guava%20and%20walnut%20trees%2C%20confident%20that%20these%20fruit-bearing%20trees%20would%20thrive%20and%20provide%20a%20good%20yield.%20But%2C%20like%20many%20ventures%2C%20things%20didn%E2%80%99t%20go%20as%20planned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20yield%20was%20not%20great%2C%20and%20I%20faced%20numerous%20challenges.%20The%20trees%20I%20planted%20were%20not%20growing%20well%2C%20and%20the%20results%20were%20disappointing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jagdish%20confesses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20giving%20up%20was%20never%20an%20option%20for%20Jagdish.%20Determined%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20he%20experimented%20with%20other%20tree%20species%20that%20could%20withstand%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20harsh%20climate.%20He%20planted%20seesham%2C%20deodar%2C%20oak%2C%20and%20rhododendron%2C%20and%20to%20his%20delight%2C%20these%20trees%20flourished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%2C%20Jagdish%E2%80%99s%20work%20was%20met%20with%20scepticism%20and%20outright%20resistance.%20The%20villagers%2C%20accustomed%20to%20traditional%20farming%20methods%2C%20were%20quick%20to%20question%20the%20wisdom%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365774%2Fradhakrishnan-nair-rk-growing-urban-forests-miyawaki-method-ecosystem-plants-green-hero-of-india-gujarat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20the%20arid%2C%20rocky%20soil%20of%20Sirkot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20used%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20the%20point%20of%20planting%20trees%20here%3F%20Nothing%20will%20grow%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20He%20kept%20pushing%20forward%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20belief%20that%20something%20better%20was%20possible%20for%20the%20land%20and%20its%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20land%20itself%20was%20as%20unforgiving%20as%20the%20doubts%20surrounding%20his%20endeavour.%20The%20farm%20was%20far%20away%20from%20his%20home%2C%20and%20every%20day%2C%20Jagdish%20had%20to%20trek%20almost%20five%20kilometres%20by%20foot%20to%20care%20for%20the%20young%20trees.%20As%20if%20that%20weren%E2%80%99t%20enough%2C%20irregular%20rainfall%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20frequent%20destruction%20of%20his%20plants%20by%20wandering%20cattle%2C%20added%20to%20his%20frustration.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20the%20cattle%20from%20the%20village%20w