%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESunday%20mornings%20were%20magical%20for%20me%20as%20a%20child.%20The%20highlight%20was%20my%20%3Cem%3Ebaba%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(grandfather)%20trip%20to%20the%20local%20vegetable%20market.%20Every%20return%20brought%20a%20familiar%20joy%20I%20yearned%20for%20%E2%80%94%20a%20new%20batch%20of%20fresh%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20greens%20and%20potatoes%20in%20his%20old%20%3Cem%3Ejhola%20%3C%2Fem%3E(bag)%2C%20there%20were%20the%20treasures%20I%20sought%3A%20%3Cem%3Ekaronda%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20cranberry)%2C%20small%20and%20jewel-like%20fruits%20in%20green%20and%20red%20hues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIgnoring%20my%20%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20(grandmother)%20gentle%20prompt%20to%20wash%20them%20first%2C%20I%E2%80%99d%20dive%20right%20in%20to%20taste%20the%20mouthwatering%20tartness.%20The%20karonda%E2%80%99s%20burst%20of%20flavour%20was%20pure%20delight%20%E2%80%94%20a%20flavour%20that%20lingered%20in%20our%20afternoon%20meals.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmma%20transformed%20these%20berries%20into%20tangy%20chutneys.%20Surplus%20harvests%20were%20pickled%2C%20preserving%20the%20summer%E2%80%99s%20bounty%20to%20enhance%20meals%20long%20after%20the%20season%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaronda%20has%20spread%20joy%20across%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20best%20part%3F%20It%20is%20easily%20grown%20at%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20your%20guide%20to%20cultivating%20this%20hardy%2C%20drought-tolerant%20fruit%20during%20the%20monsoon%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Choosing%20your%20propagation%20method%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKaronda%20can%20be%20grown%20from%20seeds%2C%20cuttings%2C%20or%20air%20layering.%20During%20monsoon%2C%20both%20cuttings%20and%20air%20layering%20can%20be%20successful.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20cuttings%2C%20take%20semi-hardwood%20cuttings%20(about%2025-30%20cm%20long).%20Whereas%20air%20layering%20method%20involves%20inducing%20roots%20